  "title": "[1-1Mentorship] Event and Sales Specialist",
  "description": "<p><strong>Looking for a career switch or breakthrough in life?</strong></p><p>Build something extraordinary for yourself through sales and marketing—away from the usual 9-5 grind!</p><p>We’re an outsourced sales and marketing company growing brand presence across industries like telecoms, non-profits, energy, and more!</p><p><strong>What You'll Do:</strong></p><p>• Use creativity to boost brand awareness through face-to-face engagements</p><p>• Build strong industry relationships</p><p>• Grow into a leadership role and inspire others</p><p><strong>What You Get:</strong></p><p>• 1-on-1 mentorship tailored for your growth</p><p>• A fun, high-energy team culture</p><p>• Travel opportunities with regional and international exposure</p><p><strong>We Want:</strong></p><p>• Professional, driven individuals with strong ethics</p><p>• Eager to learn new things with great attitude</p><p>• Team players who thrive in social settings and bring great vibes</p><p>\"Only those who dare to fail greatly can ever achieve greatly.\" – Robert F. Kennedy</p><p>Take the leap of faith with us! <strong>Apply Now</strong> and we will get to you ASAP!</p><p>(Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.)</p>",
